{"title_page": "Gujarat", "text_new": "{{pp-vandalism|small=yes}}\n{{Short description|State in western India}}\n{{About|the state in India|the city in Pakistan|Gujrat City|other uses|Gujrat (disambiguation){{!}}Gujrat}}\n{{EngvarB|date=October 2019}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2019}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n<!-- See Template:Infobox settlement for additional fields and descriptions -->\n| name                            = Gujarat<!-- Please do not add any Indic script in this infobox, per WP:INDICSCRIPT policy. -->\n| type                            = [[States and union territories of India|State]]\n| image_seal                      = Government Of Gujarat Seal In All Languages.svg\n| anthem                          = [[Jai Jai Garavi Gujarat]]<br /> \u2018\u2019Victory to Proud Gujarat\u2019\u2019\n| image                           = GujaratPhotoMontage.jpg\n| alt                             = a montage of images from Gujarat showing statues of Mahatma Gandhi and Sardar Vallabhbhai Patel, people, temples, a palace and a salt marsh \n| caption                         = From top and L-R: [[Sabarmati Ashram]], [[Gujarati people |Gujarati]] attire, [[Somnath Temple]], [[Rann of Kutch]], [[Dwarkadhish Temple]], [[Statue of Unity]], [[Laxmi Vilas Palace]] at [[Vadodara]].\n| seal_alt                        = Gujarat\n| image_map                       = IN-GJ.svg\n| map_alt                         = Gujarat in [[India]]\n| map_caption                     = Location of Gujarat in India\n| coordinates                     = {{coord|23|13|N|72|41|E|region:IN-GJ|format=dms|display=inline,title}}\n| coor_pinpoint                   = Gandhinagar\n| subdivision_type                = Country\n| subdivision_name                = {{flag|India}}\n| established_title               = Formation\n| established_date                = 1 May 1960{{ref|cap|\u2020}}\n| seat_type                       = [[Capital city|Capital]]\n| seat                            = [[Gandhinagar]]\n| seat1_